{"tid":1509513,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩屌 原來欺凌狗仔狗女會被人拉 咁玩弄感情呃蝦條始亂終棄又犯唔犯法呀","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:50:31.000Z","uid":4322,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9a147ff5a88b7caa93ef4ff9837fd8f2b0853d91","tid":1509513,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想問下玩弄感情呃蝦條（夠歲）始亂終棄扮真心朋友又犯唔犯法呀</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">扮真心想認識佢關心佢但成日無視佢又犯唔犯法呀</span></em></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地記住開學要好好關心佢地呀</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>等你地矯枉過正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n修例風波：網民發動校園欺凌警察子女　警方關注<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190823/mobile/bkn-20190823193648689-0823_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190823%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190823193648689-0823_00822_001.html&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=c5183900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190823/mobile/bkn-20190823193648689-0823_00822_001.html</